    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/dbcf232e3acb4d2b484d27c1a0634b93.poster.avif?t=1720312694\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/dbcf232e3acb4d2b484d27c1a0634b93.webm?t=1720312694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/dbcf232e3acb4d2b484d27c1a0634b93.mp4?t=1720312694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《异星战场》是一款2D战略游戏，包含了两种游戏模式：<strong>实时战略模式</strong>和<strong>战棋模式</strong>。你需要探索20多个不同单位的独特能力，积累资源，升级建筑物，灵活地放置和管理单位，以在充满挑战性的战斗中取得胜利。与电脑或其他玩家在线作战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>实时战略模式</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/a19447139d245c70d2cb56ad12e2c3ce.poster.avif?t=1720312694\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/a19447139d245c70d2cb56ad12e2c3ce.webm?t=1720312694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/a19447139d245c70d2cb56ad12e2c3ce.mp4?t=1720312694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在实时战略模式下，你必须<strong>管理你的资源、单位和时间</strong>，因为这是一个动态的游戏。试着制定你的比赛策略。你需要<strong>积累资源，升级建筑和单位</strong>，以超越对手的进度。主基地的每一次升级都将解锁新单位，你能够选择不同的升级路线，以创建不同的新单位。摧毁对方主基地的人获胜。<br>小心，因为敌人也不是在睡大觉！<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>积累和使用资源。</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>升级建筑。</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>创建和升级单位并用它们作战。</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>有20多种具有独特能力的不同单位。</strong></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战棋模式</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/f9147b12eb72d1f147c95ce936d39843.poster.avif?t=1720312694\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/f9147b12eb72d1f147c95ce936d39843.webm?t=1720312694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/f9147b12eb72d1f147c95ce936d39843.mp4?t=1720312694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在战棋模式下，游戏进行数回合，每回合分为两个阶段：<strong>准备阶段</strong>和<strong>战斗阶段</strong>。在准备过程中，您必须<strong>将有限数量的部队部署到合理的位置</strong>。尝试<strong>选择好的组合</strong>以实现最佳的战斗效果。在战斗阶段，你将不再能够控制单位，只能控制他们的能力。如果一个单位被摧毁，它就不能再参加以后的战斗。摧毁所有敌人单位的人获胜。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>合理组合单位并部署在最佳位置。</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>在战斗中使用单位技能。</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>猜测对手的部署，并合理安排克制对手的单位。</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282700/extras/207aafa97995bf5802523514c2641a00.avif?t=1720312694\" width=600 height=82 /></span>",
